{"tid":1506362,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［連登簡報會］今日勇武派手足表現英勇、克制！","createTime":"2019-08-25T18:54:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T00:33:36.000Z","uid":251001,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b0025332be123484b45852be926ad28bb4d0099b","tid":1506362,"uid":251001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T18:54:18.000Z","msg":"［序］勇武派<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">面對過千名暴徒</span></strong> 仍然於前線作戰<br />\n絲毫沒有退縮的跡象 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>勇武奮戰 緊守崗位</strong></span><br />\n在電光火石之間仍然保持應有的克制<br />\n這次行為<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>十分英勇</strong></span></span>並且<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>值得嘉許</strong></span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n//對於有暴徒使用可致命武器 表示最強烈譴責<br />\n抗爭者使用<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對等的武器還擊</span></strong>乃<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>自然反應 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n勇武抗爭者生命受到嚴重威脅下使用最低武力制止暴徒。<br />\n此外，更有暴徒多次使用警棍/致命槍械，<br />\n肆意襲擊途人嚴重破壞社會安寧。<br />\n對在場集會人士及遊人帶來極大的威脅。<br />\n有抗爭者肆意<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">踐踏</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">鄰國</span><span style=\"color: red;\">國旗</span></strong></span> 表示<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>極度讚賞</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n此舉完全體現了 當下香港的民主和自由。<br />\n晚上一批懷疑冒警人士乘坐警車於荃灣聚集，<br />\n當時試圖護送「白衣人」離開事發現場，<br />\n幸好抗爭者<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">搗破冒警人士 </span></strong>，<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">截停有關車輛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n後來有冒警人士拔除<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>非法持有的手槍</strong></span></span>指向市民<br />\n並且一度以暴力踢跌在場求饒人士，對此表示<br />\n極度憤怒。<br />\n<br />\n//激進暴徒升級的違法及暴力行為不但令人髮指，更將香港推向極為危險的邊緣，連登予以嚴厲譴責，抗爭者亦會嚴正追究。連登呼籲廣大市民共同打擊冒警人士及暴徒，維護法治，盡快回復社會秩序。 <br />\n<br />\n完<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb546e70dce095b4f4bab0192155aee6dd38a065","tid":1506362,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T18:55:36.000Z","msg":"(正經)(請給我長期置頂) 整合被控義士進程 一個也不能少不是口號！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1502159\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1502159</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"702207b1bf7655d04f4b5999fe00d5e3e97449d0","tid":1506362,"uid":277816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T18:56:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O2GaPU8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO2GaPU8.jpg&h=27ee7285&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bd620073b2669f4b412d4f892a50b8683935f6de","tid":1506362,"uid":65210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T18:56:36.000Z","msg":"［開飯/住宿/義診/搵工］你班前線死廢青 未成年中學雞同我入黎！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1503091\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1503091</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1dfc8a50bc36c974e474d290e05690a9011ad7ab","tid":1506362,"uid":96146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T18:56:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ecae94590664e52c1f6da508237214aa12e6cad","tid":1506362,"uid":279989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T00:33:36.000Z","msg":"二坡坊果度睇到好治癒!! <br />\n果班撚樣真係抵死!"}]}